# Google OAuth 2.0 Web Client ID (required).
# Create one at: Google Cloud Console > APIs & Services > Credentials > OAuth client ID (type: Web application).
# Register your app origin (e.g. http://localhost:5173 for dev, https://<project>.pages.dev for prod)
# under "Authorized JavaScript origins".
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the value. Vite only exposes vars prefixed with VITE_.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
